OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FVideo report by Hannah Norbury
OL,8,FA drinking cup that belonged to Robert
OL,9,FBurns has returned from Australia to
OL,10,Fgo on show at the farmhouse where the
OL,11,Fpoet is thought to have used it more
OL,12,Fthan 200 years ago.
OL,14,FThe cup was owned by the Taylor family
OL,15,Ffor many generations after they bought
OL,16,Fit at a sale of the poet's effects in
OL,17,F1791.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
