PN,32302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FIn the years that followed, it
OL,7,Fdescended through seven generations of
OL,8,Fthe family, who around 1805 acquired
OL,9,FEllisland Farm, the home Burns
OL,10,Fdesigned and lived in from 1788 to
OL,11,F1791.
OL,13,FEarly in the 20th century it was taken
OL,14,Fto Australia by a member of the family
OL,15,Fwho emigrated and was treated as a
OL,16,Ftreasured heirloom.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FThe cup recently surfaced at an
OL,7,Fauction in Australia and was
OL,8,Fidentified by the Robert Burns
OL,9,FEllisland Trust as an object of
OL,10,Fpotential national significance.
OL,12,FIt was bought at auction by an
OL,13,FAustralian antiques dealer and
OL,14,Fconservation work was carried out
OL,15,Fbefore it was offered for onward sale.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FThe cup has now been acquired by the
OL,7,FRobert Burns Ellisland Trust with help
OL,8,Ffrom the National Fund for
OL,9,FAcquisitions and will go on display
OL,10,Flater this month at Ellisland Museum
OL,11,Fand Farm near Dumfries.
OL,13,FAdam Dickson, project curator at the
OL,14,FRobert Burns Ellisland Trust, said:
OL,15,F"Every new piece of evidence at
OL,16,FEllisland deepens our understanding of
OL,17,Fwhat makes this place so exceptional.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,F"Objects like this are particularly
OL,7,Fprecious because they connect us
OL,8,Fdirectly to Burns's daily life."The
OL,9,Fcup has had a remarkable afterlife,
OL,10,Fand it was even used at a Burns Supper
OL,11,Fin Adelaide in 1956, where it was
OL,12,Fdrunk from by the governor of South
OL,13,FAustralia, Sir Robert George.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`OU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,F"Its journey has parallels with the
OL,7,Freach of Burns's legacy, carried
OL,8,Faround the world by the Scottish
OL,9,Fdiaspora."To have the cup back at
OL,10,FEllisland, in the room where Burns
OL,11,Fwould very likely have used it, is an
OL,12,Fextraordinary moment for the
OL,13,Fcollection and for everyone who cares
OL,14,Fabout this place."
OL,16,FThe cup is made of horn and was later
OL,17,Fembellished with a silver rim, edging
OL,18,Fand provenance plaque.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FThe trust was able to authenticate the
OL,7,Fcup against its own detailed research
OL,8,Finto the Taylor family and their
OL,9,Fdescendants, which was carried out by
OL,10,FLogan Fry, a local student who helps
OL,11,Fwith curatorial research.
OL,13,FMr Dickson said: "We are very grateful
OL,14,Fto the National Fund for Acquisitions
OL,15,Ffor making this acquisition possible
OL,16,Fand to Logan whose meticulous research
OL,17,Fhelped us prove its authenticity."
OL,26,@uD@ROUyD@bO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FThe trust is running a #12 million
OL,7,F"Save the Home of Auld Lang Syne"
OL,8,Fappeal to restore the site and secure
OL,9,Fits future.
OL,11,FThe cup arrived back in Scotland in
OL,12,FMay and is undergoing a gradual
OL,13,Facclimatisation process to minimise
OL,14,Fany impact of changes in temperature
OL,15,Fand humidity following its return from
OL,16,FAustralia.It will go on display on
OL,17,FJuly 21, the anniversary of the poet's
OL,18,Fdeath in 1796.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@aO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FThe National Fund for Acquisitions is
OL,7,Fadministered by National Museums
OL,8,FScotland on behalf of the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment.
OL,11,FDr Hazel Williamson, National Fund for
OL,12,FAcquisitions Manager at National
OL,13,FMuseums Scotland, said: "We are
OL,14,Fdelighted to support the acquisition
OL,15,Fof this cup, used by Burns at
OL,16,FEllisland Farm where he wrote some of
OL,17,Fhis most celebrated works.
OL,26,@uD@YOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
