OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,F"The support provided by the National
OL,7,FFund for Acquisitions is vital in
OL,8,Fenabling museums and other heritage
OL,9,Forganisations in Scotland to continue
OL,10,Fthe important work of preserving our
OL,11,Fshared heritage."
OL,13,FBurns wrote works such as Auld Lang
OL,14,FSyne and Tam o' Shanter while living
OL,15,Fat Ellisland.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,FDr David Hopes, trustee of the Robert
OL,7,FBurns Ellisland Trust, Head of Leeds
OL,8,FMuseums & Galleries and former
OL,9,FDirector of the Robert Burns
OL,10,FBirthplace Museum in Alloway, said:
OL,11,F"This is a genuinely important
OL,12,Facquisition for Ellisland.
OL,14,FIt is a modest object but that's what
OL,15,Fmakes it valuable to Ellisland,
OL,16,Fbecause it speaks to his daily life
OL,17,Fhere."This is a cup Burns would have
OL,18,Fdrunk from at his own table, and its
OL,19,Freturn to Ellisland is an important
OL,20,Fmoment for the wider Burns collections
OL,21,Flandscape in Scotland.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@FOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1783696745
OL,3,CRobert Burns cup returns to Scotland
OL,4,Cafter more than 100 years in Australia
OL,6,F"That the cup will go on permanent
OL,7,Fdisplay in Burns's spence, the room in
OL,8,Fwhich Burns wrote of raising a cup of
OL,9,Fkindness in remembrance of old
OL,10,Ffriends, brings a poignant symmetry to
OL,11,Fthe object's return."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOU
